===Etymology===
From {{etyl|enm|en}}, from {{etyl|fro|en}} {{term|lang=fro|remot}}, masculine, {{term|lang=fro|remote}}, feminine, from {{etyl|la|en}} {{term|lang=la|remotus}}, past participle of {{term|lang=la|removere||to remove}}, from {{term|re-|lang=la}} + {{term|movere|lang=la||to move}}.

